      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOSCATO TIME (8) missed the frame last time at Nowra but was in the finish the start prior when seventh (19.48) and goes well this course. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. KING DOUGIE (2) was prominent throughout when winning in the fastest time of the card two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 5th and beaten 5 lengths at this track (22.93). Comes out of a solid form race last start. Must be included in calculations. MAJOR TED (1) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (19.72) at this track in a Grade 5 over 340m. Overdue and expected to feature again. AIRFLOW BETTY (4) is building a nice picket fence and can add to the tally.",
